<br>
The only problem is I got extremely bored!  I actually found myself wandering to alts to have fun =(!  Now that I'm 44 (with some insurance exp) I want to do some exploring.  I've been contemplating Guk or SolB.  Any suggestions as to which is better for finding 44ish level groups?  Or any other alternatives?  No solo suggestions please.<br>
<br>
One other thing:  Research.  What a pain!  I've been auctioning for words of Convocation, Incarceration and the Essence of Rathe for what seems like forever.  If anyone on Mithaniel Marr wants to give me a hand with any spare words tonight, give me a tell =) <p>--------------------------<BR>
