<br>
Popular place on my server for pick-ups at that level seemed to be:<br>
<br>
- Dreadlands, CoM, and Karnor's Castle in Kunark.  CoM is often underhunted and is nice as you can solo in EJ if a pick-up does not happen (I don't mind soloing to fill the grouping time-gaps).  Trakanon's Teeth is nearby too.   Dreadlands are very, very good exp, but are way too popular.   Karnor's is a must-group kinda place though, lots of intense action in there -- another popular place.  A bit tough for 44th, but do-able.<br>
<br>
- East Wastes (Ry'gorr fort) /GD (Shard caves) in SoV.<br>
<br>
Never been to SolB or Guk much. <p><b>Seek Pyremaker</b><br>
Mage 51st Season, Spec-Evocation, Xegony<br>
Proud member of "The Ring of Truth"
