</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urooboynameless.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RooboyNameless</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#333333>(5/25/01 12:54:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=127.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Hit 44 last night... now what?</span><hr size=1> Well old world Sol B was THE place to go.. at 44 you can solo Kobolds there or for even better exp get in a group ie: Window room or 3 spawn. Hell Sol B was the BEST place to level to 50 Pre-expansion. <p><center><img src=http://www.users.bigpond.net.au/itwizard/WebGraphics/roologo2.jpg><br>
